		{
			description: [
				"&8[ SURVIVAL NOTE — WARMTH ]&r"
				""
				"&7The cold here is not weather. It is a condition of the world. In the earliest records, standing still is simply how people died.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: keep your body temperature up. A waterskin and a way to read the cold will buy you time to learn everything else.&r"
			]
			icon: "cold_sweat:waterskin"
			id: "7A01000000000104"
