		{
			description: [
				"&8[ SURVIVAL NOTE — FOOD ]&r"
				""
				"&7Raw scavenging will not sustain a person here for long. The old kitchens I have catalogued were elaborate. Ours will start smaller.&r"
				""
				"&8Objective: build a cooking pot and a cutting board. Cook something worth eating.&r"
